code: public FakeProxySelector addProxy(Proxy proxy) {     proxies.add(proxy).     return this. }

@Override public List<Proxy> select(URI uri) {     // Don't handle 'socket' schemes, which the RI's Socket class may request (for SOCKS).     return uri.getScheme().equals("http") || uri.getScheme().equals("https") ? proxies : Collections.singletonList(Proxy.NO_PROXY). }
@Override public void connectFailed(URI uri, SocketAddress sa, IOException ioe) { }
